title: Javed Kausar wins PP-8 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Javed Kausar an independent candidate has won the election from Punjab Assembly constituency PP-8 Rawalpindi-II by securing 47,526 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was PPPP Khurram Pervez Raja who bagged 40,603 votes.
The votersâ€™ turnout remained 45.88 %.
